Enum Mode backed by u8 has small be 0; large be 1.

To match owned mode: Mode, giving i32.
Let result be 0.
Match mode:
Mode.small: Let cells be owned buffer of 2 i32 filled with 5; result becomes cells at 0;
Mode.large: Let cells be owned buffer of 4 i32 filled with 9; result becomes cells at 3;
otherwise: result becomes 1.
Give result.

To main, giving i32.
Give match owned Mode.large.
